Protouch is Montreal Furniture Assembly company specializing in installation and assembly of practically any type of furniture and appliances. We service residential and commercial clients as well as furniture retailers in the Montreal Area. Our assembly expertise includes home, office and garden furniture, exercise equipment, appliances and anything else that needs our Pro Touch.

Our Montreal furniture assembly team help you with any assembly and installation challenge for your home, office or commercial space.
